name: Pfam domain graphics
body:
# Pfam domain graphics - jQuery

This ports over the script used by generate graphic tool from pfam to use jQuery instead of prototype for use in the WormBase website.

Not fully tested.
tagline: port the domain_graphics javascript library from Pfam to work using jQuery instead of prototype. For use on WormBase.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
